          <title>Shopify CEO Tobi Lutke Introduces AI Mandate: Employees Must Prove Need for New Hires</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Shopify's CEO, Tobi Lutke, has introduced a new mandate requiring employees to prove the need for new hires before adding staff. The move aims to utilize artificial intelligence (AI) to augment team capabilities and streamline business processes.]]></description>
